! Everforest Theme for CodeMirror 6

Green-based warm color palette based on [[Everforest|https://github.com/sainnhe/everforest]].

Designed to be easy on the eyes with nature-inspired colors.

!! Variants

* `everforest` / `everforest-dark` - Dark (default)
* `everforest-dark-hard` - Higher contrast dark
* `everforest-light` - Light

!! Available Theme Classes

| !Class | !Description |
| `cm6-theme-everforest` | Dark (default) |
| `cm6-theme-everforest-dark` | Same as above |
| `cm6-theme-everforest-dark-hard` | Dark hard |
| `cm6-theme-everforest-light` | Light |
